Jackpot¶

jackpot.views.confirm_jackpot(request)[source]¶

This method will get lucky pick id and verify the lucky pick id. If verification is successful then will return the url of confirm_jackpot html page.

Parameters

  • name – request - used to generate responses(Http) depending on the request that it receives

  • type – HttpResponse

Returns

returns posts page

jackpot.views.make_jackpot(request)[source]¶

This method will return the url of make_jackpot html page.

Parameters

  • name – request - used to generate responses(Http) depending on the request that it receives

  • type – HttpResponse

Returns

returns posts page
